The '''Sociedad Tolkien Chilena''' ("Chilean Tolkien Society") or '''STC''', is the [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien Society]] in Chile. It was established in 1998.<ref>[http://www.sociedadtolkienchilena.cl/web/concilio-blanco/ Concilio Blanco] at [http://www.sociedadtolkienchilena.cl  sociedadtolkienchilena.cl] (accessed 6 April 2023)</ref>
==Publications==
The society publishes the journal ''Mae Govannen''. As of 2020, 17 issues had been published.<ref>[http://www.sociedadtolkienchilena.cl/web/ique-es-mae-govannen/ ¿Qué es Mae Govannen?] at [http://www.sociedadtolkienchilena.cl  sociedadtolkienchilena.cl] (accessed 6 April 2023)</ref>
